column5: Well as you can See I finally broke down and got a website---having said this though---I'll continue to share the fishing related work with everyone here.  Just Complete......"Back To The Farm"  (Click on image to make bigger)  Bushart
Looks lonely. The boy needs a puppy tagging along beside him. Nice work.
Well I had a couple cats runnin behind him but it made a distraction--so I took them out---it's simplicity made me like it--clean and quiet
looks good, has kind of a depressing atmosphere looks like a storms coming and hes alone
looks like hes gonna have a good dinner tho, maybe a 6-pack in his other hand
Being the owner of one of Terrance's photos I have to say I am extremely pleased...  And will be calling him again... soon.  G
Please use me as a reference Terrance... I got exactly what I wanted and you worked with me to make it happen.  G
Thanks Gerritt  Glad to be able to help out---I actually painted a portrait of my dawg when I had some time since yours.
